  <sec id="s3">
    <title>Results</title>
    <sec id="s3-s1">
      <title>Data in the DAPredict database</title>
      <p>DAPredict contains a total of 1748 approved drugs, 454 ADRs, 178 ATCs and 111 428 061 compounds. Among them, 178 ATCs covered all 14 first-level ATCs, and compounds covered 168 360 natural products. All relationship pairs are counted as shown in <xref rid="T1" ref-type="table">Table 1</xref>; there are 305 981 drug-ADR relationships and 83 117 drug-ATC relationships. A total of 5808 pairs of substructure-ADR relationships, 1748 pairs of substructure-ATC relationships, 33 334 pairs of substructure-domain relationships, 30 874 pairs of domain-ADR relationships and 2788 pairs of domain-ATC relationships came from our prediction algorithm.</p>
