$$Score = {{\Sigma }}_{j = 1}^{j = n}Co{r_{sub\,i\, - \,domain\,j}}*Co{r_{domain\,j\, - \,ADR\,or\,ATC}}$$\end{document}</tex-math>
      </disp-formula>
