      <p>Since the prediction of compounds is performed online, it is impossible to obtain the relationship score between all compounds and phenotypes in advance to construct the background, and the approved drugs that have been predicted in advance are representative of all compounds, so the score thresholds of the online prediction were set consistent with the approved drugs.</p>
